        We run the complete GEO checklist as part of every AI visibility audit — technical foundations, entity audit, content structure review, and monitoring setup, delivered as a prioritised remediation plan with 90-day milestones.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col items-center gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
